After three minutes, though,

00:03:10.083 --> 00:03:10.916 line:71%
they can start the fire.

00:03:10.916 --> 00:03:12.000 size:84% position:42% line:71%
So a very quick

00:03:12.000 --> 00:03:14.041 position:59% line:71%
he's taking us to an Israeli community

