a winding mountain road,

00:03:20.750 --> 00:03:23.000 position:58% line:71%
past a roadblock in a security fence

00:03:23.000 --> 00:03:25.375 line:71%
and into the village of Shula,

00:03:25.375 --> 00:03:27.750 position:61% line:71%
which sits right on the Lebanese border.

