00:03:54.375 --> 00:03:57.375 line:71%
missile right here,

00:03:57.375 --> 00:03:58.458 size:84% position:42% line:71%
past the window.

00:03:58.458 --> 00:03:59.333 size:75% position:38% line:71%
Two homes,

00:03:59.333 --> 00:04:00.791 line:71%
one next to the other,

00:04:00.791 --> 00:04:02.583 line:71%
hit in the same attack.

00:04:02.583 --> 00:04:04.875 position:56% line:71%
According to the Israeli military,

00:04:04.875 --> 00:04:06.666 position:61% line:71%
this is one of the most dangerous places

00:04:06.666 --> 00:04:07.458 line:71%
in northern Israel.

00:04:07.458 --> 00:04:08.708 line:71%
Right now, we're in Shula,

00:04:08.708 --> 00:04:10.833 position:58% line:71%
and you can see the Lebanese border

00:04:10.833 --> 00:04:12.458 line:71%
just right across there, across

00:04:12.458 --> 00:04:14.125 line:71%
from those concrete barriers.

00:04:14.125 --> 00:04:15.666 line:71%
We're just a few hundred feet.

00:04:15.666 --> 00:04:16.833 line:71%
And what that means

00:04:16.833 --> 00:04:18.291 line:71%
is that we are within range

00:04:18.291 --> 00:04:20.166 position:58% line:71%
of those anti-tank guided missiles.

00:04:20.166 --> 00:04:21.416 line:71%
And that is exactly

00:04:21.416 --> 00:04:23.125 position:56% line:71%
what has wrought this destruction

00:04:23.125 --> 00:04:24.500 line:71%
on this civilian home.

00:04:24.500 --> 00:04:26.125 line:71%
The threat of anti-tank

00:04:26.125 --> 00:04:27.208 line:71%
missiles is part of

00:04:27.208 --> 00:04:28.041 size:75% position:38% line:71%
why Israel

00:04:28.041 --> 00:04:29.208 line:71%
wants to push Hezbollah

00:04:29.208 --> 00:04:32.333 position:61% line:71%
back to the Litani River, about 18 miles

00:04:32.333 --> 00:04:33.791 line:71%
north of the border,

00:04:33.791 --> 00:04:36.250 position:58% line:71%
outside the range of those missiles.

00:04:37.041 --> 00:04:39.833 line:71%
Okay, we have 35 seconds.

00:04:39.833 --> 00:04:41.291 position:56% line:71%
We've been here for three minutes.

00:04:41.291 --> 00:04:43.375 position:61% line:71%
The colonel has been watching his watch

00:04:43.375 --> 00:04:45.416 position:59% line:71%
the entire time that we've been here.

00:04:45.416 --> 00:04:48.416 position:61% line:71%
And now he's telling us it's time to go.

