Hezbollah has been firing rockets,

00:04:51.500 --> 00:04:53.000 line:71%
missiles and drones

00:04:53.000 --> 00:04:55.666 position:59% line:71%
at northern Israel since October 8th.

00:04:55.666 --> 00:04:56.958 line:71%
Israel has responded

00:04:56.958 --> 00:04:57.833 size:84% position:42% line:71%
with air strike

00:04:57.833 --> 00:04:59.125 size:84% position:42% line:71%
after airstrike,

00:04:59.125 --> 00:05:01.708 position:59% line:71%
devastating parts of southern Lebanon,

00:05:01.708 --> 00:05:03.208 line:71%
where more than 90,000

00:05:03.208 --> 00:05:04.750 line:71%
