00:05:18.166 --> 00:05:19.250 size:88% position:44% line:71%
the first people.

00:05:19.250 --> 00:05:20.958 line:71%
Israel settled in Shula

00:05:20.958 --> 00:05:22.875 size:88% position:44% line:71%
in the late 1960s,

00:05:22.875 --> 00:05:24.416 line:71%
and after spending his summers

00:05:24.416 --> 00:05:25.666 size:88% position:44% line:71%
there as a child,

00:05:25.666 --> 00:05:27.708 line:71%
Ori decided to move there.

00:05:27.708 --> 00:05:28.208 size:81% position:41% line:71%
Meaning there

00:05:28.208 --> 00:05:29.708 position:56% line:71%
still is a special place for you.

