Of course I wouldn't.

00:05:37.250 --> 00:05:38.041 size:81% position:41% line:71%
I would have,

00:05:38.041 --> 00:05:39.041 line:71%
and the first moment

00:05:39.041 --> 00:05:40.833 line:71%
I would have been to. Yeah.

